parameters:
General Atu: It seems like everyone is here. Although...
there are some uninvited guests as well.

Palace Official Emoni: The appearance of dragons is a crisis
for the empire! Queen Caron-sama is also concerned about the
situation.

Palace Official Emoni: As a representative of the palace, I
will participate. There is a possibility that the strategy
proposed by the Adventurer's Guild may fail.

Profligate Noble Lud I was just asked by Clea-chan, so it's
not like I wanted to come. But there are a bunch of invoices
coming in, is this some kind of joke?
Maid Amina: Please fulfill your role as a wallet properly.

General Atu: Hmph, you're a nuisance, but I'll let it slide
today.

General Atu: The current situation is extremely bad. The
soldiers are exhausted from repeated battles.

General Atu: The supplies were prepared by those useless
noble idiots over there, but there is no doubt that we will
be at a disadvantage if the battle becomes prolonged.

Guild Leader Agonia: Then let's prepare quickly and proceed
with the operation as soon as the magic academy's magicians
have prepared the airship.

Guild Leader Agonia: Our role is crucial in buying time for
the airship to take off safely.

Guild Leader Agonia: And our mission is to fight against the
dragons and pave the way for Clea and the others.

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: What if Clea and the others
are killed by the dragons?

Guild Leader Agonia: We will kill the dragons, eliminate the
threat to the empire, and avenge our members. We will
absolutely not let them escape.

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: You're lucky, you can die in
peace.
Clea: Yes, I will definitely kill them.

Stolge of Affection: The academy members have arrived now!
It seems that both the airship and the crystal are in good
condition.

Stolge of Affection: It seems that we can fly tomorrow
morning at the fastest speed.

General Atu: We will execute the operation tomorrow morning!
I want everyone to thoroughly prepare for battle.

General Atu: Tomorrow's operation is unlike anything in the
long history of the empire. Let us be grateful for the
opportunity to make a name for ourselves in history.

General Atu: We will definitely make a path! Go and take the
dragon's head without worry!

Guild Leader Agonia: The key to this operation is Clea.
Please prepare without any regrets.

Stolge of Affection: Don't push yourself too hard, okay?
After all, life is something that can't be taken back.

Royal Court Official Emoni: To be in the same space as
Agonia... how unpleasant.

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: 'After I'm done with you guys,
I'll take on the dragon. Don't worry about what happens
next, just die in peace.'

The profligate noble, Luid, said, 'It's been a while since I
looked at a bill and felt sick. I sincerely pray for the
success of Clea and the others.'
Maid Amina: I pray for your good fortune.
Guild Leader Agonia: Let's prepare to go back as well.

Stolge of Affection: Since there is a possibility of
encountering goblins on the way, we will make sure to safely
escort the two of you.

Stolge of Affection: You want to stay by Clea's side, don't
you?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes... I want to stay by her side,
even if it's just for a little while.

Celis of the Swift Wind: I think it's what Clea needs the
most right now... to have someone stay by her side.

Guild Leader Agonia: The dragon is dead, and the revenge is
over.

Guild Leader Agonia: But the days will continue. Protecting
and fighting for someone's daily life is what the
Adventurer's Guild, Futera, is all about.
Guild Leader Agonia: Let's go back to our daily lives.
実績 英雄の歌：ドラゴン討伐
実績 ドラゴンスレイヤー
